<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>إِلَيْكَ جُنَّ الْعَشَرَهْ ... إِنَّ عَلَيْهِ نُفَرَهْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>ثَعَالِبًا وَهِرَرَهْ ... وَحِيضًا مِنْ سَمُرَهْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَقِطْعَةً مِنْ نَمِرَهْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَوْلُهُ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا، وَالدَّمِ مَا هُوَ بِشَاعِرٍ»</span> قَالَ: هِيَ يَمِينٌ كَانَ يُحْلَفُ بِهَا فِي الْجَاهِلِيَّةِ "<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>